            <h1 id="ebStoryHeadline" class="eb-article__headline" data-eb-story-headline="Geopolitical standoff in South China Sea results to environmental fallout">
                Geopolitical standoff in South China Sea results to environmental fallout
            </h1>
        </div>

        <div class="eb-article__standfirst-wrapper">
            
                <h2 class="eb-article__standfirst">Satellite images show significant growth in the occurrence of algal blooms in contested areas in the South China&nbsp;Sea.</h2>
            
        </div>
        

        
